 3492 万人、 3091 万人、 3592 万人，增长率分别为 8.0% 、 7.3% 和 7.3%，成为用户规模增长最快的三类应用。我国网民规模达 10.79 亿人，互联网普及率达 76.4%| 界面新闻 · 快讯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c1ea3804dc369dbfad3de0c405c0a3d2_xl.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "25 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/619502802"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIlfyYotHd1a9ZEAMaCDk5OTQ3MzQxIJr+sKcGMAA4wwNAHnIJNjE5NTAyODAyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1693339356.44353", "card_id": "Q_315635424", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 186}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "高校教师和科研人员有没有中年危机？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "本题已加入知乎圆桌 »科研有点难，更多研究生和科研人关心的话题，欢迎关注。 出于交叉学科的本能，想到这个奇怪问题。请见谅 比如，原学科领域遇到瓶颈，而转变研究方向不容易？ 或者，有成功转变研究方向，甚至比之前做得更得意的栗子？ 比如，随学科发展，想做的问题越来越艰深复杂，自身力不从心，而学生又不给力？ 或者，成功找到很厉害的学生，合作愉快，走出瓶颈的栗子？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-4a0efafa42b5d029d42087f02295fdf5_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "25 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/315635424"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IlfyYotHd1a9ZEAMaCDMyNDE3NzA5IImHnuQFMAA4iSFAH3IJMzE1NjM1NDI0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1693339356.44919", "card_id": "Q_614444438", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 49}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "想买一块上班戴的手表，有哪些设计经典、不易过时的手表款式？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f37d6b80c963151b2a3023fbafca3795_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "24 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "htt